import React from 'react'
import { PrimaryNav, Nav, ResIcon, NavLink, Hamburger, MenuLink } from '../../pure/Navelements';

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <PrimaryNav>
                <Hamburger />
                <Nav>
                    <MenuLink to="/home" activeStyle>
                        Home
                    </MenuLink>
                    <MenuLink to="/product" activeStyle>
                        Product
                    </MenuLink>
                    <MenuLink to="/details" activeStyle>
                        Details
                    </MenuLink>
                    <MenuLink to="/contact" activeStyle>
                        Contact
                    </MenuLink>
                </Nav>
            </PrimaryNav>
        </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
